# Cursor Configuration for Render MCP Integration

## MCP Server Setup
- Use the MCP server configuration in `mcp-server-config.json`
- Connect to Render services through MCP protocol
- Enable direct deployment and management capabilities

## Render Integration
- Access Render dashboard through MCP
- Deploy applications directly from Cursor
- Monitor deployment status and logs
- Manage environment variables and settings

## Development Workflow
- Use MCP to check Render service status
- Deploy code changes automatically
- Monitor application performance
- Access Render logs for debugging

## Commands Available
- Deploy to Render
- Check service status
- View logs
- Update environment variables
- Scale services
